recurrence.types.monthly.comment: Example: 'Monthly on the first Friday'. Translate only uppercase in 'MONTHLY ON THE {week, select, 1 {FIRST} 2 {SECOND} 3 {THIRD} 4 {FOURTH} other {LAST}} {day}'

recurrence.types.cron.comment: Repeats the schedule email using custom cron expression defined by the user. Do not translate word 'Cron' as it is a name of technical specification.

recurrence.types.inherit.comment: Repeats the schedule email using the same recurrence as the setup in parent.

recurrence.cron.tooltip.comment: Do not translate html tags , . Do not translate 'unix-cron' as it is a name of specific tech.
